[
  {
    "start": 0.48,
    "end": 8.24,
    "text": "Welcome to English listening channel.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 4.799,
    "end": 10.88,
    "text": "Hello everyone. Today we are going to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 8.24,
    "end": 13.759,
    "text": "watch  a story about visiting a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 10.88,
    "end": 16.96,
    "text": "doctor and a pharmacy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 13.759,
    "end": 20.16,
    "text": "In this video you will follow a simple",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 16.96,
    "end": 24.88,
    "text": "conversation between two  friends",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 20.16,
    "end": 27.84,
    "text": "Ken and Ellie. Ken is not feeling well.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 24.88,
    "end": 31.119,
    "text": "So he goes to a clinic, talks with a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 27.84,
    "end": 33.04,
    "text": "doctor, and later visits a pharmacy to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 31.119,
    "end": 34.239,
    "text": "get medicine.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 33.04,
    "end": 37.6,
    "text": "Don't worry, ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 34.239,
    "end": 41.52,
    "text": "everything is spoken slowly and clearly",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 37.6,
    "end": 44.64,
    "text": "so you can relax and enjoy the story.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 41.52,
    "end": 48.239,
    "text": "Before we start, I have a small question",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 44.64,
    "end": 52.64,
    "text": "for you. Please listen carefully to find",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 48.239,
    "end": 55.44,
    "text": "the answer. Here is today's question.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 52.64,
    "end": 58.559,
    "text": "What symptoms does Ken have this",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 55.44,
    "end": 61.12,
    "text": "morning? The answer appears in the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 58.559,
    "end": 63.52,
    "text": "conversation.  If you find the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 61.12,
    "end": 66.56,
    "text": "answer, please write it in the comments",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 63.52,
    "end": 69.439,
    "text": "section. Writing your answer in English",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 66.56,
    "end": 72.32,
    "text": "is a great way to practice. ",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 69.439,
    "end": 74.96,
    "text": "All right, are you ready? Let's begin",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 72.32,
    "end": 78.72,
    "text": "the story.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 74.96,
    "end": 80.24,
    "text": " Hey, Ken, are you okay? You don't look",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 78.72,
    "end": 83.36,
    "text": "so good.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 80.24,
    "end": 84.479,
    "text": " Hey, Ellie. Yeah, I don't feel well",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 83.36,
    "end": 88.4,
    "text": "today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 84.479,
    "end": 91.84,
    "text": " Oh no, what's wrong? You look tired.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 88.4,
    "end": 94.96,
    "text": " I have a headache and my throat is sore.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 91.84,
    "end": 97.119,
    "text": " A headache and a sore throat. That",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 94.96,
    "end": 99.92,
    "text": "doesn't sound good.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 97.119,
    "end": 102.0,
    "text": " Yeah, it started this morning. When I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 99.92,
    "end": 105.439,
    "text": "woke up, I had a headache.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 102.0,
    "end": 108.079,
    "text": " Oh, that's not good. And how about your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 105.439,
    "end": 109.36,
    "text": "throat? When did your throat start",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 108.079,
    "end": 112.32,
    "text": "hurting?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 109.36,
    "end": 114.56,
    "text": "My throat started hurting last night. I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 112.32,
    "end": 116.24,
    "text": "thought it was nothing, but now it",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 114.56,
    "end": 118.479,
    "text": "really hurts.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 116.24,
    "end": 121.04,
    "text": " Do you have a fever?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 118.479,
    "end": 124.479,
    "text": " I'm not sure, but I think I have a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 121.04,
    "end": 127.84,
    "text": "little fever. My body feels warm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 124.479,
    "end": 130.0,
    "text": " Let me touch your forehead. Yeah, you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 127.84,
    "end": 132.239,
    "text": "feel a little warm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 130.0,
    "end": 135.68,
    "text": " Really? I thought so.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 132.239,
    "end": 138.879,
    "text": " Ken, I think you might have a cold.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 135.68,
    "end": 140.56,
    "text": " A cold? Maybe you're right. I feel",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 138.879,
    "end": 143.04,
    "text": "tired, too.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 140.56,
    "end": 145.84,
    "text": " You should see a doctor.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 143.04,
    "end": 147.68,
    "text": " Uh,  I think I'm okay. Maybe I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 145.84,
    "end": 151.2,
    "text": "just need some rest.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 147.68,
    "end": 154.48,
    "text": " No, Ken. You have a headache, a sore",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 151.2,
    "end": 158.0,
    "text": "throat, and a fever. You should really",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 154.48,
    "end": 160.72,
    "text": "see a doctor. It's better to go now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 158.0,
    "end": 162.64,
    "text": " But I don't like going to the doctor. I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 160.72,
    "end": 166.0,
    "text": "always feel nervous.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 162.64,
    "end": 168.8,
    "text": " I know, but your health is important.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 166.0,
    "end": 170.56,
    "text": "Don't worry. I'll go with you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 168.8,
    "end": 173.519,
    "text": " You will come with me?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 170.56,
    "end": 175.519,
    "text": " Of course. There's a clinic near here.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 173.519,
    "end": 177.84,
    "text": "Let's go together.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 175.519,
    "end": 178.879,
    "text": " Okay, you're right. Let's go to the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 177.84,
    "end": 182.64,
    "text": "clinic.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 178.879,
    "end": 185.599,
    "text": " Good. Let's go now before it gets late.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 182.64,
    "end": 186.8,
    "text": " Thanks, Ellie. I feel sick, but I'm glad",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 185.599,
    "end": 189.76,
    "text": "you're here.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 186.8,
    "end": 192.239,
    "text": " Of course. That's what friends are for.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 189.76,
    "end": 196.159,
    "text": "Let's go.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 192.239,
    "end": 197.44,
    "text": " Excuse me. I would like to see a doctor,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 196.159,
    "end": 201.04,
    "text": "please.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 197.44,
    "end": 203.36,
    "text": " Of course. Welcome to our clinic. Is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 201.04,
    "end": 206.48,
    "text": "this your first time here?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 203.36,
    "end": 209.2,
    "text": " Yes, this is my first time.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 206.48,
    "end": 210.319,
    "text": " Okay. What seems to be the problem",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 209.2,
    "end": 214.319,
    "text": "today?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 210.319,
    "end": 215.84,
    "text": " I have a sore throat and I think I have",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 214.319,
    "end": 219.92,
    "text": "a fever.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 215.84,
    "end": 223.44,
    "text": " I see. Do you have any other symptoms?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 219.92,
    "end": 226.879,
    "text": " Yes, I also have a headache.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 223.44,
    "end": 230.48,
    "text": "Okay. When did your symptoms start?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 226.879,
    "end": 233.519,
    "text": " My throat started hurting last night and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 230.48,
    "end": 236.72,
    "text": "my headache started this morning.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 233.519,
    "end": 240.0,
    "text": " Thank you. Do you have an appointment?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 236.72,
    "end": 241.2,
    "text": " No, I don't have an appointment. Is that",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 240.0,
    "end": 244.4,
    "text": "okay?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 241.2,
    "end": 246.879,
    "text": " That's fine. We can see you today, but",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 244.4,
    "end": 249.599,
    "text": "you may need to wait a little.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 246.879,
    "end": 252.64,
    "text": " That's okay. I can wait.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 249.599,
    "end": 255.92,
    "text": " Great. First, I need you to fill out",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 252.64,
    "end": 258.72,
    "text": "this form. Please write your name, date",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 255.92,
    "end": 262.079,
    "text": "of birth, and your symptoms.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 258.72,
    "end": 264.96,
    "text": " Okay, I will fill out this form.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 262.079,
    "end": 266.72,
    "text": " Take your time. When you finish, please",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 264.96,
    "end": 267.919,
    "text": "bring it back to me.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 266.72,
    "end": 270.16,
    "text": " Sure.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 267.919,
    "end": 271.199,
    "text": " Do you have your insurance card with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 270.16,
    "end": 274.16,
    "text": "you?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 271.199,
    "end": 277.04,
    "text": " Yes, I have it. Here you go.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 274.16,
    "end": 280.0,
    "text": " Thank you. I'll copy this and give it",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 277.04,
    "end": 282.639,
    "text": "back to you. After that, please have a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 280.0,
    "end": 284.56,
    "text": "seat in the waiting room. The doctor",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 282.639,
    "end": 287.44,
    "text": "will call your name.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 284.56,
    "end": 290.639,
    "text": " The waiting room is over there.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 287.44,
    "end": 293.919,
    "text": " Yes, right over there. Please sit down",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 290.639,
    "end": 296.72,
    "text": "and wait. We will call you soon.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 293.919,
    "end": 300.8,
    "text": " How long do I need to wait?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 296.72,
    "end": 303.44,
    "text": " Maybe about 15 or 20 minutes. There are",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 300.8,
    "end": 307.36,
    "text": "a few patients before you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 303.44,
    "end": 309.919,
    "text": " Okay, that's fine. Thank you very much.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 307.36,
    "end": 311.919,
    "text": "You're welcome. I hope you feel better",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 309.919,
    "end": 315.6,
    "text": "soon.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 311.919,
    "end": 317.52,
    "text": "Hello, I'm Dr. Miller. Please come in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 315.6,
    "end": 319.36,
    "text": "and sit down.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 317.52,
    "end": 323.36,
    "text": " Thank you, doctor.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 319.36,
    "end": 326.16,
    "text": " So, Ken, what brings you here today? Can",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 323.36,
    "end": 329.12,
    "text": "you tell me about your symptoms?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 326.16,
    "end": 330.24,
    "text": " Yes. I have a headache and my throat",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 329.12,
    "end": 333.36,
    "text": "hurts.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 330.24,
    "end": 336.32,
    "text": " I see. When did it start?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 333.36,
    "end": 338.16,
    "text": " It started this morning. When I woke up,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 336.32,
    "end": 341.36,
    "text": "I had a headache.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 338.16,
    "end": 343.36,
    "text": " Okay. And your throat? When did your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 341.36,
    "end": 345.919,
    "text": "throat start hurting?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 343.36,
    "end": 348.4,
    "text": " My throat started hurting last night,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 345.919,
    "end": 351.919,
    "text": "but it got worse this morning.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 348.4,
    "end": 355.6,
    "text": " I understand. Do you have a fever?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 351.919,
    "end": 359.44,
    "text": " I think so. My body feels warm.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 355.6,
    "end": 365.199,
    "text": " Let me check your temperature. Okay. You",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 359.44,
    "end": 366.479,
    "text": "have a slight fever. It's 37.8°. 8° C.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 365.199,
    "end": 368.56,
    "text": " I see.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 366.479,
    "end": 371.68,
    "text": " Do you have a cough?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 368.56,
    "end": 372.8,
    "text": " A little bit. Not a lot, but sometimes I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 371.68,
    "end": 375.52,
    "text": "cough.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 372.8,
    "end": 377.28,
    "text": " Do you have a runny nose?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 375.52,
    "end": 379.44,
    "text": " Yes, a little.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 377.28,
    "end": 382.96,
    "text": " Do you feel tired?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 379.44,
    "end": 386.72,
    "text": " Yes, I feel very tired today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 382.96,
    "end": 391.44,
    "text": " Okay, let me look at your throat. Please",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 386.72,
    "end": 394.8,
    "text": "open your mouth and say ah. Uh,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 391.44,
    "end": 398.24,
    "text": " I can see your throat is red. It looks",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 394.8,
    "end": 399.919,
    "text": "like you have a cold. It is probably a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 398.24,
    "end": 402.8,
    "text": "common cold.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 399.919,
    "end": 406.479,
    "text": " Just a cold. That's good to hear.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 402.8,
    "end": 409.28,
    "text": " Yes, a cold is not serious, but you need",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 406.479,
    "end": 411.759,
    "text": "to take care of yourself. If you don't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 409.28,
    "end": 414.639,
    "text": "rest, it can get worse.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 411.759,
    "end": 417.6,
    "text": " I understand. What should I do?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 414.639,
    "end": 419.919,
    "text": " I will write you a prescription. You can",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 417.6,
    "end": 422.639,
    "text": "take it to a pharmacy and get your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 419.919,
    "end": 425.599,
    "text": "medicine. The medicine will help with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 422.639,
    "end": 427.28,
    "text": "your headache and your sore throat.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 425.599,
    "end": 430.72,
    "text": " Thank you, doctor.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 427.28,
    "end": 434.16,
    "text": " Also, please make sure to rest. Stay",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 430.72,
    "end": 436.08,
    "text": "home and sleep a lot. Don't go to work",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 434.16,
    "end": 438.639,
    "text": "for a few days.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 436.08,
    "end": 442.16,
    "text": " Okay, I will rest at home.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 438.639,
    "end": 444.72,
    "text": " And please drink a lot of water. It is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 442.16,
    "end": 448.8,
    "text": "very important to drink water when you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 444.72,
    "end": 450.16,
    "text": "are sick. I understand. Rest and drink a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 448.8,
    "end": 453.36,
    "text": "lot of water.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 450.16,
    "end": 456.08,
    "text": " That's right. Here is your prescription.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 453.36,
    "end": 458.4,
    "text": "Please take this to a pharmacy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 456.08,
    "end": 460.319,
    "text": " A pharmacy? Okay.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 458.4,
    "end": 463.199,
    "text": " The pharmacy will give you your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 460.319,
    "end": 466.0,
    "text": "medicine. If you don't feel better in a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 463.199,
    "end": 467.199,
    "text": "few days, please come back and see me",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 466.0,
    "end": 469.28,
    "text": "again.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 467.199,
    "end": 470.479,
    "text": " How many days should I wait before I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 469.28,
    "end": 473.759,
    "text": "come back?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 470.479,
    "end": 476.639,
    "text": " If you still feel sick after 5 days,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 473.759,
    "end": 479.599,
    "text": "please come back. But most people feel",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 476.639,
    "end": 482.479,
    "text": "better in three or four days.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 479.599,
    "end": 484.16,
    "text": " I understand. I will. Thank you very",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 482.479,
    "end": 487.44,
    "text": "much, Dr. Miller.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 484.16,
    "end": 488.639,
    "text": " You're welcome. Take care, Ken. Get well",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 487.44,
    "end": 492.639,
    "text": "soon.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 488.639,
    "end": 496.639,
    "text": " Thank you. I will take care of myself.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 492.639,
    "end": 498.24,
    "text": " Hey, Ken. How did it go? What did the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 496.639,
    "end": 502.24,
    "text": "doctor say?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 498.24,
    "end": 506.08,
    "text": " It went well. The doctor was very nice.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 502.24,
    "end": 507.84,
    "text": " Good. So, what did the doctor say about",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 506.08,
    "end": 510.72,
    "text": "your symptoms?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 507.84,
    "end": 514.88,
    "text": " The doctor said I have a cold.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 510.72,
    "end": 517.36,
    "text": " A cold? I thought so. Did the doctor",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 514.88,
    "end": 520.56,
    "text": "give you any medicine?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 517.36,
    "end": 523.519,
    "text": " Well, the doctor didn't give me medicine",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 520.56,
    "end": 524.88,
    "text": "directly, but the doctor gave me a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 523.519,
    "end": 528.8,
    "text": "prescription.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 524.88,
    "end": 531.519,
    "text": " Oh, a prescription. That makes sense.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 528.8,
    "end": 534.399,
    "text": "You need to take the prescription to a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 531.519,
    "end": 537.12,
    "text": "pharmacy to get the medicine.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 534.399,
    "end": 539.519,
    "text": " Yes, that's right. The doctor said I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 537.12,
    "end": 542.88,
    "text": "should take it to a pharmacy.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 539.519,
    "end": 546.32,
    "text": " Did the doctor say anything else?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 542.88,
    "end": 548.72,
    "text": " Yes, the doctor told me to rest at home",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 546.32,
    "end": 552.0,
    "text": "and drink a lot of water.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 548.72,
    "end": 554.959,
    "text": " That's good advice. Rest is very",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 552.0,
    "end": 558.0,
    "text": "important when you have a cold.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 554.959,
    "end": 560.56,
    "text": " Yeah. The doctor also said I should not",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 558.0,
    "end": 564.24,
    "text": "go to work for a few days.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 560.56,
    "end": 567.92,
    "text": " That's a good idea. If you go to work,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 564.24,
    "end": 570.32,
    "text": "other people might catch your cold, too.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 567.92,
    "end": 571.839,
    "text": " That's true. I don't want to make other",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 570.32,
    "end": 575.36,
    "text": "people sick.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 571.839,
    "end": 579.519,
    "text": " Right. You should listen to the doctor.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 575.36,
    "end": 583.92,
    "text": "So, do you know where a pharmacy is?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 579.519,
    "end": 587.12,
    "text": " H not really. Is there one near here?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 583.92,
    "end": 590.08,
    "text": "Yes, there is a pharmacy just down the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 587.12,
    "end": 592.8,
    "text": "street. Let's go there now.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 590.08,
    "end": 595.92,
    "text": " Okay, let's go to the pharmacy and get",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 592.8,
    "end": 597.92,
    "text": "my medicine. I hope it's not too far.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 595.92,
    "end": 601.279,
    "text": "I'm really tired.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 597.92,
    "end": 605.2,
    "text": " Don't worry, it's very close. Just a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 601.279,
    "end": 608.399,
    "text": "2inut walk from here. Let's go. I'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 605.2,
    "end": 609.519,
    "text": "walk with you. You still don't look so",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 608.399,
    "end": 612.56,
    "text": "well.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 609.519,
    "end": 614.399,
    "text": " Huh? Thanks, Ellie. I'm lucky to have a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 612.56,
    "end": 617.12,
    "text": "friend like you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 614.399,
    "end": 619.12,
    "text": " Don't mention it. Let's just get you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 617.12,
    "end": 622.079,
    "text": "better.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 619.12,
    "end": 624.24,
    "text": " Hello. I have a prescription from my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 622.079,
    "end": 627.04,
    "text": "doctor. Here you are.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 624.24,
    "end": 628.959,
    "text": " Hello. Thank you. Let me take a look at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 627.04,
    "end": 632.24,
    "text": "your prescription.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 628.959,
    "end": 634.64,
    "text": "Okay, I see. The doctor prescribed two",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 632.24,
    "end": 637.04,
    "text": "kinds of medicine for you. I will",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 634.64,
    "end": 640.959,
    "text": "prepare your medicine now. Please wait a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 637.04,
    "end": 643.68,
    "text": "moment. Sure. Thank you. Okay. Here is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 640.959,
    "end": 646.72,
    "text": "your medicine. You have two kinds of",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 643.68,
    "end": 649.839,
    "text": "medicine. This one is for your headache",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 646.72,
    "end": 650.959,
    "text": "and fever. And this one is for your sore",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 649.839,
    "end": 654.56,
    "text": "throat.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 650.959,
    "end": 657.279,
    "text": " I see. Two kinds of medicine. Can I ask",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 654.56,
    "end": 660.16,
    "text": "you some questions about the medicine?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 657.279,
    "end": 663.04,
    "text": " Of course. Please ask me anything.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 660.16,
    "end": 665.839,
    "text": " How often should I take this medicine?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 663.04,
    "end": 668.959,
    "text": " You should take both medicines twice a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 665.839,
    "end": 672.8,
    "text": "day. Once in the morning and once in the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 668.959,
    "end": 676.32,
    "text": "evening. Twice a day, morning and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 672.8,
    "end": 678.959,
    "text": "evening. Got it. Should I take it before",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 676.32,
    "end": 681.76,
    "text": "meals or after meals?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 678.959,
    "end": 683.92,
    "text": " Please take the medicine after meals. It",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 681.76,
    "end": 685.839,
    "text": "is better for your stomach. Taking",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 683.92,
    "end": 688.16,
    "text": "medicine on an empty stomach can",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 685.839,
    "end": 691.76,
    "text": "sometimes make you feel sick.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 688.16,
    "end": 694.079,
    "text": " After meals. Okay, I understand. Are",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 691.76,
    "end": 696.72,
    "text": "there any side effects?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 694.079,
    "end": 699.12,
    "text": "Some people feel a little sleepy after",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 696.72,
    "end": 701.519,
    "text": "taking this medicine. So please be",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 699.12,
    "end": 705.2,
    "text": "careful if you are driving.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 701.519,
    "end": 706.399,
    "text": " I might feel sleepy. Okay, I will be",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 705.2,
    "end": 708.72,
    "text": "careful.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 706.399,
    "end": 710.8,
    "text": " Yes. So it is better to take the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 708.72,
    "end": 713.44,
    "text": "medicine when you are at home.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 710.8,
    "end": 714.88,
    "text": " That makes sense. I am going to rest at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 713.44,
    "end": 717.44,
    "text": "home anyway.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 714.88,
    "end": 719.68,
    "text": " Also, please don't drink alcohol while",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 717.44,
    "end": 723.36,
    "text": "you are taking this medicine.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 719.68,
    "end": 725.839,
    "text": " No alcohol. I understand. And one more",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 723.36,
    "end": 728.639,
    "text": "thing, please finish all of your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 725.839,
    "end": 731.839,
    "text": "medicine. Even if you feel better, don't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 728.639,
    "end": 734.56,
    "text": "stop. Take it until it is all gone.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 731.839,
    "end": 737.92,
    "text": " I should finish all of the medicine. Got",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 734.56,
    "end": 741.12,
    "text": "it. How long should I take the medicine?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 737.92,
    "end": 743.44,
    "text": " You have 5 days of medicine. So, please",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 741.12,
    "end": 747.92,
    "text": "take it for 5 days.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 743.44,
    "end": 748.959,
    "text": " 5 days. Twice a day after meals for 5",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 747.92,
    "end": 751.04,
    "text": "days.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 748.959,
    "end": 753.76,
    "text": " That's correct. And don't forget to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 751.04,
    "end": 755.44,
    "text": "drink a lot of water. Water helps the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 753.76,
    "end": 757.839,
    "text": "medicine work better.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 755.44,
    "end": 759.68,
    "text": " I will drink a lot of water. Thank you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 757.839,
    "end": 761.6,
    "text": "very much for your help.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 759.68,
    "end": 763.92,
    "text": " You're welcome. I hope you feel better",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 761.6,
    "end": 765.92,
    "text": "soon. If you have any other questions",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 763.92,
    "end": 767.44,
    "text": "about the medicine, you can always come",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 765.92,
    "end": 770.639,
    "text": "back and ask.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 767.44,
    "end": 772.8,
    "text": " Thank you. I appreciate it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 770.639,
    "end": 777.36,
    "text": " Did you get your medicine?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 772.8,
    "end": 780.399,
    "text": " Yes, I did. I got two kinds of medicine.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 777.36,
    "end": 783.04,
    "text": "One is for my headache and fever. The",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 780.399,
    "end": 786.639,
    "text": "other one is for my sore throat.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 783.04,
    "end": 788.88,
    "text": " Good. So, how do you take the medicine?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 786.639,
    "end": 791.76,
    "text": "Let me help you remember.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 788.88,
    "end": 794.399,
    "text": " Okay. The pharmacist said I should take",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 791.76,
    "end": 798.56,
    "text": "the medicine twice a day.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 794.399,
    "end": 800.399,
    "text": " Twice a day. So, once in the morning and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 798.56,
    "end": 803.04,
    "text": "once in the evening.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 800.399,
    "end": 805.279,
    "text": " Yes, that's right. And I should take the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 803.04,
    "end": 808.639,
    "text": "medicine after meals.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 805.279,
    "end": 811.76,
    "text": " After meals. That's important. Don't",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 808.639,
    "end": 814.079,
    "text": "take it on an empty stomach. Okay.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 811.76,
    "end": 816.639,
    "text": " Right. The pharmacist said taking",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 814.079,
    "end": 818.24,
    "text": "medicine on an empty stomach can make",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 816.639,
    "end": 821.76,
    "text": "you feel sick.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 818.24,
    "end": 824.399,
    "text": " Good. What else did the pharmacist say?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 821.76,
    "end": 827.279,
    "text": " The pharmacist said I might feel a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 824.399,
    "end": 829.2,
    "text": "little sleepy after taking the medicine.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 827.279,
    "end": 832.48,
    "text": "That's a side effect.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 829.2,
    "end": 835.2,
    "text": " Oh, you might feel sleepy. Then you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 832.48,
    "end": 837.44,
    "text": "should probably just rest at home.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 835.2,
    "end": 840.48,
    "text": "That's perfect.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 837.44,
    "end": 841.76,
    "text": " Yeah, I guess so. And I should not drink",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 840.48,
    "end": 844.72,
    "text": "alcohol.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 841.76,
    "end": 848.24,
    "text": " No alcohol while you're taking medicine.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 844.72,
    "end": 850.24,
    "text": "Got it. And don't forget to drink a lot",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 848.24,
    "end": 853.44,
    "text": "of water, right?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 850.24,
    "end": 856.24,
    "text": " Yes. Both the doctor and the pharmacist",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 853.44,
    "end": 858.8,
    "text": "told me to drink a lot of water.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 856.24,
    "end": 862.079,
    "text": " Water is really important when you're",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 858.8,
    "end": 864.48,
    "text": "sick. How many days do you need to take",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 862.079,
    "end": 868.0,
    "text": "the medicine? I need to take the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 864.48,
    "end": 870.8,
    "text": "medicine for 5 days. The pharmacist said",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 868.0,
    "end": 872.16,
    "text": "I should finish all of it, even if I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 870.8,
    "end": 875.279,
    "text": "feel better.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 872.16,
    "end": 876.32,
    "text": " That's really important. Don't stop",
